prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D illustration for a birthday card, whimsical and humorous with a beautiful botanical style. At the center of the composition, a cartoon-style air fryer is depicted as a magical, glowing treasure chest, slightly open with a golden light emanating from within. Floating out of the air fryer are whimsical illustrations representing Jordan's loves: a perfectly fried egg on a cloud of fluffy white rice, a friendly cartoon robot waving, and a glowing lightbulb symbolising problem-solving. Surrounding this central scene is an elaborate and lush botanical frame made of detailed green leaves, ferns, and delicate white flowers, weaving elegantly around the elements. In the bottom corners, nestled amongst the leaves, are two small, charming icons: on the left, a tiny illustrated restaurant menu, and on the right, a simple brain-teaser puzzle icon. The entire scene is set against a clean, soft cream background. In the open center space, the text "Happy Birthday, Jordan!" is written in a beautiful, readable, dark green handwritten cursive script. The overall feeling is a clever, personal, and artful tribute to his unique interests.
